    "asOf": "2007-05-24",
    "date": "2007-06-27T19:41:00Z",
    "text": "Amends the Internal Revenue Code to provide for the tax treatment of a charitable remainder pet trust as a charitable remainder annuity trust. Defines \"charitable remainder pet trust\" as a trust which pays a specified annual amount (for a maximum term of 20 years) for the care of domesticated companion animals living at the time of creation of the trust."
